  "notes": "Live Shopify 2026-04 evidence for discount connection mechanics after public local-write setup. The recorder creates two scheduled DiscountCodeBasic records and two scheduled DiscountAutomaticBasic records with title order intentionally opposite creation/GID order, bulk-adds three redeem codes to one code discount, waits until the scheduled catalog windows match the disposable titles, captures reverse first/after discountNodes pages, TITLE ordering for discountNodes/codeDiscountNodes, CREATED_AT reverse ordering for automaticDiscountNodes (Shopify's automatic root exposes only CREATED_AT and ID sort keys), discountNodesCount(limit:) AT_LEAST precision, and nested DiscountRedeemCodeConnection nodes/edges/pageInfo. Proxy replay uses the same public create and bulk-add mutations, then reads only through GraphQL roots; IDs and opaque cursors are treated as volatile while ordering, pageInfo booleans, count precision, and redeem-code windows are strict."
